title: Tragically Hip - We Are the Same
description:
The Tragically Hip is a Canadian rock band from Kingston, Ontario, consisting of Gordon Downie (lead vocals and guitar), Paul Langlois (guitar), Rob Baker (guitar), Gord Sinclair (bass) and Johnny Fay (drums).

The band is a popular and influential band in Canada. Their acclaimed 2000 album Music at Work won Best Rock Album at the 2001 Juno Awards, as did their 1998 album Phantom Power at the 1999 Junos. In 2005 they were inducted into the Canadian Music Hall of Fame.
